== 威脅 ==
儘管令人喜愛，但持續的盜捕和貿易走私加上棲地受到破壞已對野外的非洲灰鹦鹉數量產生極大影響；其中盜捕及貿易走私是造成野外的非洲灰鹦鹉數量迅速下降的最大主因，光是 1993 至 2003 年間就有超過 35.9 萬隻非洲灰鹦鹉在國際市場上進行交易，有人質疑當中許多筆貿易可能屬於非法，這些鸚鵡大多來自[[喀麥隆|喀麥隆]]、[[剛果|剛果]]以及[[象牙海岸|象牙海岸]]<ref>CITES. [http://www.cites.org/eng/com/ac/22/E22-10-2-A1.pdf ''Psittacus erithacus''] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130512093433/http://www.cites.org/eng/com/ac/22/E22-10-2-A1.pdf |date=2013-05-12 }}. 2006. AC22 Doc.10.2. Annex 1. pp.3–22.</ref>，然而這樣的進口鸚鵡死亡率非常高<ref name = parrotcaptive/><ref>{{cite web | title = "Trade in Africa' s Grey Parrots and Timneh Parrots is currently not sustainable" | url = http://www.birdlife.org/datazone/sowb/casestudy/568 | publisher = State of the world's birds. BirdLife International | accessdate = 10 April 2014 | archive-date = 2013-11-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20131109044856/http://www.birdlife.org/datazone/sowb/casestudy/568 | dead-url = no }}</ref>；目前全球約有 56 萬隻野生非洲灰鸚鵡，活動範圍約 2,760,000 平方公里<ref name = "birdlife">{{ cite web | title = "Species factsheet: ''Psittacus erithacus'' " | url = http://www.birdlife.org/datazone/speciesfactsheet.php?id=112657 | author = [[國際鳥盟|國際鳥盟]]物種說明 | accessdate = }}</ref>。
